title: Bug 121170: 'getColumnLabel' should return recognizable strings before data extraction
description: The 'getColumnLabel' function in the IMetaData object is returning null for labels before data extraction, but after extraction, it returns recognizable strings.
OB: The labels returned before extraction are null, while the ones after extraction are recognizable strings.
EB: The 'getColumnLabel' function in the IMetaData object should return recognizable strings for all columns, including before data extraction.
SR: To reproduce the issue, call the 'getColumnLabel' function on the IMetaData object before and after data extraction. Compare the results and observe that the labels before extraction are null.
